Package: datacamp 
Type: Package 
Title: Easily create interactive courses for datacamp.com with R Markdown 
Version: 0.1 
Date: 2013-09-07
Author: Jonathan Cornelissen and Ramnath Vaidyanathan 
Maintainer: Jonathan Cornelissen <Jonathan@datacamp.com>
Description: This package makes it easy and fun to create interactive courses for www.datacamp.com. Use R Markdown (and the slidify style) documents to write exercises. Easily add interactivity with build-in functionality to write simple Submission Correctness Tests.
License: MIT 
URL: www.datacamp.com 
Depends:
  datacampSCT,
  slidify, 
  RCurl, 
  httr,
  RJSONIO,
  XML,
  yaml